{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_52b3d8c17729b6f8efc49991",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一条鱼和一份礼物",
        "text_hash": "21ae6c588ab6099aebd4f3289486b166491b8c36f70f8c3d32b8c97d106670f2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9a24b7480f23f7d2de3865cd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "优素福和爸爸互相击掌。",
        "text_hash": "5ff6de87ed3b9527e2e53ad28e55755f2a7a983f4b5393b65d44b6b990515707",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6b8918790f7d7548d9b25ea0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在一个特别的星期五，天空还没有亮起一丝微光，优素福的父亲就穿好了衣服。他穿上厚厚的防风雨夹克，戴上能盖住耳朵的绿色羊毛帽。他向儿子挥手告别。当爸爸说：“今天就是我要抓一条鱼，并给你带一份礼物回家的日子。”优素福的眼睛亮了起来。",
        "text_hash": "55c1fd95e6b4034c3e86dd63c329780ad5eb4c5a6b5d1a1c5055435b862b768c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c7733eaf65f49777e6615525",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸骑着自行车去海滩。",
        "text_hash": "fec815040244b3a75d74cbc2e0194c7aaf2b91f534d368ec0465abafbe5ed62a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_220e210c5558295819eeed93",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一条鱼和一份礼物？哦，会是什么呢？爸爸骑车前往穆伊岑贝格海滩。车轮一路吱呀吱呀地响着，直到冲浪者角。",
        "text_hash": "a0067e91b765700335e0e6500af47fe7a237a4191f820882bbbebe6dcdaa7ad6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_df3561a92f1ec34d2d68ae54",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "海鸥在空中盘旋。“什——么？什——么？什——么？”它们叫着。“你会给优素福带回什么？”",
        "text_hash": "c1490bba6391fe3a337f0b4aeeac0cca1797e411b7463b1f5d81f9bb93f87d2f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d6b5c616ee1b1cc4baeca9ba",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸按响车铃。“等等看会是什么吧！”",
        "text_hash": "381e0101b2a8e67efc9ffc56aaeff23145288c2d6b44bd5bb246b04751ebed89",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_91681d5ee8a7f9d398ad0b7f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸向准备出海的渔民们挥手。",
        "text_hash": "1610e75f60b4533960b3fd52f58e54b4d04b03c962b6652fd8129b9e20887b59",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0c5df51bcbed5852bf2dcfb5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "渔民们看着太阳升起。他们检查渔网。他们检查船桨。他们倾听风声。他们把船拖到水边。优素福的祖父，欧帕·萨利，曾是一名拉网渔民。在他之前，他的父亲欧帕格罗特吉·里德万也熟悉大海。",
        "text_hash": "efe4898c32a4a4bbfde1abd4429bab9c9f8724edf11a5a8dceb08a881f5ba213",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8907d6566814a9e78ac96640",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸和其他渔民一起出海。",
        "text_hash": "3d329633da937dc7eb384fc519d4ee4173f27450b9c9a0c8c3ef5f408849994c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c9e4ebe6ce6e54254568baaf",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小船驶入海浪。爸爸的手臂伸向船桨。他的腿抵住船舷。他的脖子绷紧，背部肌肉起伏。",
        "text_hash": "fc6d9df37f77b830a20c951851e6bbb09a927fb88396cd5b95cfa5a2fe6a9880",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ee6e225dd79a91b985af994c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸一边干活一边唱：“落下又划开。找到一条鱼。拉起又扑通。千万别停下。”",
        "text_hash": "34e7b365717c828a524b9cdc9859f4d168607504968f2f5dcaa8d6738ab9919d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_53307f37adf1b0db8badee32",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "优素福查看爸爸给他带来的礼物。",
        "text_hash": "472009ce4a6de87e2a0667a66acccfb5c2803951c06fa51c0be370b34734e33c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ec8023779826892f25f9e6ff",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一整天，优素福都望着天空。天空明亮、晴朗，也没有风。一条鱼和一份礼物！爸爸会从海上带什么回家呢？有时他会带回一个美丽的贝壳。有时他会带回一个被海浪冲洗过的宝石般绿色的瓶子。",
        "text_hash": "b542e7b76c6958500f2b9101b45edbedc6390a607d4303059a4cd3b34719b257",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_616fa480711ba551e6fd6d57",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸和海龟们站在海滩上。",
        "text_hash": "c6d68d8b755c87ae2cd8a2206a3d6817194c528d473575914d94dab95f72c4fa",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_56f4af6e36a10b0cbff8d517",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有些日子，优素福的父亲会带回一个故事。比如有一次，他们在沙滩上发现了海龟，数百只海龟在暴风雨中被冲上了岸。",
        "text_hash": "c31f287abef4b3e07ba8925317f9553d49e45240831106bf982e70cc45cea858",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3ab9a003bac89afead78f18d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“什——么？什——么？什——么？”海鸥叫着。“你们会做什么来帮助这些海龟？”",
        "text_hash": "c091184434d8c4cf1ca472db107abb5aeeabf47cd7cc00ccf54ef354451ab16c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c1227ed1f34e590fc0a6613e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸说：“我们救了那些海龟，我跟你说实话。我们把它们送回了大海，一只不落。”",
        "text_hash": "28927b339e6b44ff5e90cac5c4ef00a23a3f0bc250aac111703202ab187c3737",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3f1463cdb73f83ab6cbdd16a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "海滩上的拉网渔民。",
        "text_hash": "822b6443e5444c6d0733850416fdce135c2704f44b6273b90dea68e13d325b9b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_49258aed06d0a10950a0a022",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸总会带回一首歌。他拉船桨时唱着这首歌。他拉渔网时唱着这首歌。他缠绕绳索时唱着这首歌。他骑车回家时也唱着这首歌。“落下又划开。找到一条鱼。拉起又扑通。千万别停下。”",
        "text_hash": "e2228795ef3c287f1af5e5d82cb139c061caaf92af28139378623d41954fe9d5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d80f91aaf2f41ee005e9e37f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "萨菲娅奶奶和优素福走去迎接爸爸。",
        "text_hash": "b9373149c7518c52e6e9a085b912826fc212f2ce6c3aa9335c49e444031b823a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_290cb26f687b45336bc669de",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "萨菲娅奶奶想要一条漂亮肥美的黄尾鱼做晚餐。妈妈想要一条新裙子。",
        "text_hash": "46a5b8e1dcd3b5d44aa7613325e08fa2b5b9f04fad172d1e58940471d2386acd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_344b21e2830ea1464618aded",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“别傻了，”奶奶说。“如果他们哪怕抓到一只小螃蟹，你就算幸运了。更有可能的是星期五只有鱼尾巴吃。海里的鱼已经没有那么多了。”",
        "text_hash": "617af6073c1c2708206db04764024f2bee9a347ffa8f2017ae1d1fc18aa5a0dd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_80034ae748b813054a57872c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "优素福牵着奶奶的手。他们在更衣小屋旁过马路。",
        "text_hash": "8bbc9fc322118a70d3935441d064f128b5c72b3746a3956f83797b0788bf4261",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_853dfc1a12866a8260e6d415",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“什——么？什——么？什——么？”停在鲜亮屋顶上的海鸥叫着。“晚餐吃什么？”",
        "text_hash": "6b57e96cd3f2234684025c67e66df14dc7080efaf571b9376caa5a41b0c666bf",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_037a55cbaca26b533d6e33d9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸在海滩上与一名冲浪者对峙。",
        "text_hash": "e0355d5e7dfb2c180fdf2951231cc1aaf517dce320d1bfd2084ef367f987d1c9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3428cd7089ba359ebe176c97",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "去年，渔民们和冲浪者发生了争执。有人愤怒地挥拳，有人大声叫喊。",
        "text_hash": "8402562038bb85794a5e6550f9ed246bd4fc4a59aa4639402ae29b9bc6f56db3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_dba4173b6aa445ddcb342c68",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“什——么？什——么？什——么？”海鸥叫着。",
        "text_hash": "729f71eaeed8108ffbbc911994dc8816507e3eab43c7b384659b8e6155e8421d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d994893cd09c8705849801c2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“大海足够每个人使用，”优素福的父亲说。他给他们看了曾属于欧帕·萨利的捕鱼许可证。“海浪属于所有人。海水免费共享。”",
        "text_hash": "81795ce5cab97babaddd11b816ccc37fd445d2a4858019f4049be9536180a544",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_125115bdfbd220cb441ad3cb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "萨菲娅奶奶和优素福在海滩上等爸爸。萨菲娅奶奶用望远镜看着远处。",
        "text_hash": "a61316638b18ff0b6797853cd9f007bfbd0b76617bb05b71502b67ddb33d62ae",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ebe7ef1ae8c2274fe846ce73",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "萨菲娅奶奶透过望远镜观看，手指因好奇而蜷起。鲨鱼警报响了。游泳的人跑回沙滩，抓起毛巾。冲浪者夹着冲浪板冲向岸边。他们在淋浴处脱下潜水服。",
        "text_hash": "60d3531e7ea69051240d3ec178576402233af7bc16b358df4a59d2eba7b3cdf4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_db84ad993e344e9b3a48312e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“什——么？什——么？什——么？”海鸥叫着。“优素福的父亲会从海里带回什么？”",
        "text_hash": "60ef4521593a4d733b84d7c86111e5a7e9d008c9c63a47e4c5aefc6c6a4e8835",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_08bd25a57e40a4df3213294d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸在网里发现了一条鲨鱼。",
        "text_hash": "184ca053f07d3041f75570de25e374669d14ccc8a6eb8172a4a06804388e154c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ba62295b3de5478af65363fd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "优素福的父亲、叔叔和表兄弟们用力拖拽。一条小鲨鱼被困住了。它在浪中扭动挣扎。优素福的父亲一边解开渔网，一边对鲨鱼唱着：“落下又划开。找到一条鱼。拉起又扑通。千万别停下。”",
        "text_hash": "887bed0044a91e046d573e57c4daef089f35ca69f68289e54a6f0b8db49a0586",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ccd55f032def91ed9c082fa0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "当鲨鱼终于获得自由时，它飞快地冲回海浪里，网中只留下一条肥美的黄尾鱼。萨菲娅奶奶会高兴的。",
        "text_hash": "250ce3cef4f899833c862869443e6ef5e102a8d6a9e4b638e7db080ac972f35e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d513b4abb6594ca4c62739b5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸送给优素福的礼物是一颗鲨鱼牙齿。",
        "text_hash": "5b6e4770d57680a76650e5543a045372e1ff15fd7cab7943bb77904717535580",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ea53c25ddff2674130b29a46",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "男人们把船拉上岸，把缆绳盘起来。一个坚硬的白色三角形碰到了爸爸的手指。",
        "text_hash": "5ddccd05ea62a5c66093cca279f11dec1e7ff9ce97bf7ddfa87ac4ab747c0bf4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e90b74b1c26a254d23d901bc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“什——么？什——么？什——么？”海鸥叫着。“你给优素福带回了什么？”",
        "text_hash": "61641dfc0117667da4297d52f0fa09d414113b7536b93107ea3499320603294f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_df14ed1302b0aa2ff72dada4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "太阳落山时，爸爸回答了海鸥。“给我儿子的一颗幸运鲨鱼牙。”",
        "text_hash": "7c5c4dec0ab96ed6a844b87c6020714667d7256a85c6d7708b0a6e5cc001c80c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b8aa6c92d8e0c50b00852267",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在家里，优素福把他的礼物举向星空。",
        "text_hash": "f3a955ae9a78e6b2f13a08d02e3bdc9d955d9e92d5c475e673e2e59345c41533",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_ae17d621bc8759cde79aa1eb"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
